Hi Jasper, 


Well spotted, there was a limiter of 100 for the front end display, we have lifted this limit and now all of the votes are being seen. If you refresh your page you will be able to see them now. 


FYI there have a been a total of 714 votes so far, of which 325 were collected once the email confirmation process has been added. 


Thanks and speak soon,

Morning team!


I have a few questions regarding the voting for the Battle of the Labs. Is the voting capped at 100? No videos have over 100 votes so I went to vote for one of them, I then received a pop up saying I had to input my email address, I did that and a confirmation email with a link was sent to me.


I clicked the link to confirm my vote and it said my vote was counted.


I then went back to the landing page and the tally for the video hadn’t changed. I re-freshed the landing page but still nothing changed.


Attached are the screen grabs so you can see what was happening.


Thanks
